    BSgenome.Hsapiens.UCSC.hg19.masked,
    testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Encoding: UTF-8
biocViews: Genetics, ChIPSeq, DNASeq, MethylSeq, CopyNumberVariation
NeedsCompilation: no
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
